headline: Consumers Energy Connects with Kalamazoo Community to Help Customers Reduce Energy Use and Save Money
summary: Consumers Energy is marking the progress of its "Count on Us Kalamazoo!" initiative Saturday, September 13 during an "Energizing Equity" event in Kalamazoo as part of the energy provider's commitment to energy waste reduction in some of its most underserved communities.
